  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p548948/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><div>\n\t</div>\n<p>\n\tDiapers and Kindles delivered to your doorstep not by truck, not by plane or train &mdash; but by <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/drone\" target=\"_blank\">drone</a>?你能想象一架无人机，而不是卡车、飞机或火车，将你订购的尿布、电子阅读器送到你家门口吗？</p>\n<p>\n\tAmazon CEO Jeff Bezos says that this reality may be just four or five years away.亚马逊网站首席执行官杰夫&middot;贝索斯称，这一远景有望在四、五年内成为现实。</p>\n<p>\n\tIn a interview with Charlie Rose on CBS&rsquo;s &ldquo;60 Minutes&rdquo; Bezos showed off Amazon-branded drones that he says can travel 10 miles and carry packages weighing up to five pounds to doorsteps in less than 30 minutes.杰夫&middot;贝索斯日前做客CBS电视台的《60分钟》新闻节目，在与主持人查理&middot;罗斯的交谈中，杰夫展示了亚马逊研发的无人机。他称这台无人机可以在30分钟之内行驶10英里距离，将5磅重以下的包裹送货上门。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201312/001606af2830495cab7508f030765ace.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;These are octocopters,&rdquo; Bezos said in the interview. &ldquo;These are effectively drones, but there&rsquo;s no reason these can&rsquo;t be used as delivery vehicles.&rdquo;&ldquo;这是一种八翼无人机，&rdquo;贝索斯在采访中说，&ldquo;它们是非常有效率的无人机，没有什么理由它们不能用来送货。&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\tYou won&rsquo;t be seeing them anytime soon &mdash; the FAA has yet to release rules about how <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/unmanned\" target=\"_blank\">unmanned</a> flying vehicles may be used &mdash; but Bezos said he thinks Amazon could start offering a &ldquo;Prime Air&rdquo; service within four or five years.这种无人机目前还不会被广泛应用，还有待联邦航空局对无人驾驶飞行器的行为规范做出相关规定。但是贝索斯称，四、五年内亚马逊就应该可以开始提供这种&ldquo;Prime Air&rdquo;服务。</p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;It will work, and it will happen,&rdquo; Bezos said. The truth is that the FAA will ultimately decide that.贝索斯说，&ldquo;这种运输方式不仅行之有效的，而且具备现实的条件。&rdquo; 此言是否属实，最终还得须由联邦航空局来决定。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p548948/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p548948\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548568/\">《速度与激情》男主角保罗&bull;沃克车祸身亡</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543864/\">只剩30天：年底前必须完成的3件事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548143/\">突击传统文化词汇，迎接四六级段落翻译</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548878/\">四六级备考月第六周：考前10天最后突击</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548160/\">骆驼也卖萌！不请自来与主人共进早餐</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548140/\">BBC看中国：仅6%中国人表示对工作很投入</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p547741/\">凛冬已至！关于冬季保暖的10件事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548925/\">美国宇航员登月曾寻嫦娥：带大兔子的可爱姑娘</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p548908/\">四六级新题型模考卷免费做：万人模考活动进行中！</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
